gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 126, Wizards 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Wizards, 126-107. Jaylen Brown (36 points, six rebounds) and Jayson Tatum (33 points, six rebounds, three assists) combined for 69 points as Kristaps Porzingis totaled 15 points, six rebounds, and three assists for Boston. Kyle Kuzma went 9-15 for 21 points, five rebounds, and four assists for Washington.
